window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A razor-sharp thriller that fuses ancient history with high-stakes espionage, <i>Lost Secret: The Hidden Truth of Nalanda</i> will leave you breathless.</p> <p>When intelligence officer Kabir is sent to Rajgir to recover from a personal tragedy, he doesn’t expect to be thrust into a conspiracy that could rewrite the global power structure. A sniper’s bullet, a cryptic inscription, and a murdered archaeologist catapult him into a perilous chase across India’s ancient sites.</p> <p>Teaming up with fiery historian Reeya Ghosh, Kabir uncovers secrets buried for millennia: the legendary wootz steel and its lost connection to the clean and abundant thorium energy. Hunted by mercenaries and mistrusted by their own, they must race against time to stop a forgotten technology from igniting a new era of domination and chaos.</p> <p>Thrilling, intelligent and disturbingly plausible, Lost Secret unearths the forgotten past to confront the future and keeps you turning pages long into the night.</p>"; 
